      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "🎨 PRESENTATION LAYER - Frontend\n\nNext.js 14+ (App Router) | React 18+ | TypeScript | TailwindCSS\nComponents: Dashboard, BOQ Upload, Carbon Analysis, Certification View\nState: Redux/Zustand | Real-time: WebSocket/SSE",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🎨 PRESENTATION LAYER - Frontend\n\nNext.js 14+ (App Router) | React 18+ | TypeScript | TailwindCSS\nComponents: Dashboard, BOQ Upload, Carbon Analysis, Certification View\nState: Redux/Zustand | Real-time: WebSocket/SSE",
