      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "🚀 API LAYER - Backend Services\n\nFastAPI (Python 3.12+) | RESTful + GraphQL | JWT Auth | CORS\nEndpoints: /upload, /analyze, /calculate, /certify, /export\nMiddleware: Auth, Logging, Rate Limiting, Error Handling",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "🚀 API LAYER - Backend Services\n\nFastAPI (Python 3.12+) | RESTful + GraphQL | JWT Auth | CORS\nEndpoints: /upload, /analyze, /calculate, /certify, /export\nMiddleware: Auth, Logging, Rate Limiting, Error Handling",
