      "text": "🧠 INTELLIGENCE LAYER - AI Agent Orchestration\n\nLangGraph State Machine | 12 Specialized Agents | Supervisor Router\nAgents: Material, Carbon, Sustainability, Compliance, BOQ, Certification\nAI: OpenAI GPT-4 | Vector DB: Embeddings | NLP: spaCy",
