      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "💾 DATA LAYER - Persistence & Knowledge\n\nPostgreSQL (Relational) | Redis (Cache) | GraphDB (Materials Knowledge)\nModels: Projects, BOQs, Materials, CarbonData, Certifications\nMigrations: Alembic | ORM: SQLAlchemy | Query: SPARQL (GraphDB)",
