      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "📝 Architecture Notes:\n• Layered architecture with clear separation of concerns\n• Each layer communicates only with adjacent layers (no layer-skipping)\n• Cross-cutting concerns (auth, logging) span all layers via middleware\n• Stateless design with Redis for caching and session management",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "📝 Architecture Notes:\n• Layered architecture with clear separation of concerns\n• Each layer communicates only with adjacent layers (no layer-skipping)\n• Cross-cutting concerns (auth, logging) span all layers via middleware\n• Stateless design with Redis for caching and session management",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 72,
      "index": "aK",
      "autoResize": true
    }
